{"tid":1680091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬鞍山有幼兒園爆發上呼吸道感染　20名學童受感染","createTime":"2019-10-28T14:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T15:17:22.000Z","uid":125193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa0b91bea3bee551fa09d68c6532fe5c56ec7e2","tid":1680091,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:52:45.000Z","msg":"2019-10-28 HKT 22:38<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">位於馬鞍山的香港浸信會聯會利安幼兒園，爆發上呼吸道感染個案，20名學童受感染，年齡2至5歲。<br />\n<br />\n他們<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">上月3日</span></strong>起出現發燒、咳嗽和流鼻水等上呼吸道感染病徵。17人已求醫，其中6人需入院，經治療後已出院。所有病人現時情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n6名學童的呼吸道樣本經化驗後，證實對腺病毒呈陽性反應。衞生防護中心人員已視察該校，並提供預防呼吸道感染的建議。該校正接受醫學監察。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488698-20191028.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488698-20191028.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP7Y5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=b2e592b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488698-20191028.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5fce81f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488698-20191028.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f6758bea4a6a742a971e3a9f0b6e5a34d98121a5","tid":1680091,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:54:19.000Z","msg":"20個人非法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1778b3e6d491d7982e3c5cb71f9c25ef3d2fb9ae","tid":1680091,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:54:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"244fefb51539373e82c04568dce2fd2cca5021e9","tid":1680091,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T14:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fd36e81c994980fcd2f6c4b